name: test_errors1
description:
This function tests if the alert appears when trying to create an empty quiz.

        Logs in with the credentials of 'creator1' and goes to the quiz creation page

        Presses the Submit button.
        If there wasnt an alert within a second the test is considered failed.
        It also prints if the page has changed from the quiz creation one.

        If there was an alert but the page changed anyways, the test also fails

labels.name: story
labels.value: Testa se aparece um alerta quando se cria um teste vazio
